name: Experiment Or Die #102
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. There have been too many large generative projects that have done poorly in the last few weeks. It's a mixture of flippers playing the mints slow and likely causing a poor mint by stunting the momentum, and collectors being more cautious because of numerous scams and rugpulls. 2022 is going to be the year of the artist and art for arts sake. And sometimes you just want some stunning colors and sweeping lines. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
